spec.name: Quobba Building
spec.description:
🔻 Architect: Pierre Gosset
🔻 Dates: 1915
🔻 Current Status: Cultural Center
🔻 Comments: It was originally part of the Moroccan-French Exposition in what is now Marche Central. When Marche Central construction started, the Quobba was moved as is to Arab League Park.
